proper implantation.

04:17.156 --> 04:20.023
Why do I have
this T-shaped uterus?

04:20.093 --> 04:21.993
Well, probably has something
to do with medication

04:22.060 --> 04:24.757
that was given to your mother
when she was pregnant with you.

04:24.831 --> 04:26.264
We used lot of drugs
back in the '70s

04:26.332 --> 04:29.392
which we now know
can cause infertility.

04:29.469 --> 04:30.731
Infertility?

04:30.803 --> 04:35.035
Yeah. I would say that your
chances of conceiving are very low.

04:35.108 --> 04:36.132
How low?

04:36.209 --> 04:38.234
Well, I don't want to
assign a number to it.

04:38.311 --> 04:42.304
What would you assign it?
A color, a nickname, a locker?

04:42.415 --> 04:43.609
Okay.

04:43.683 --> 04:45.708
One in a million.

04:48.421 --> 04:50.514
I just don't like...

04:50.590 --> 04:52.387
