were in vitro.

05:27.360 --> 05:28.725
Have you considered adoption?

05:28.795 --> 05:30.786
I have applied
for an adoption, yes.

05:30.863 --> 05:34.299
Kate, please don't get
a black baby.

05:35.301 --> 05:36.962
Well, I don't think we'll
have to worry about that,

05:37.036 --> 05:38.936
because for a single woman,

05:39.005 --> 05:40.734
it can take about five
years to get an adoption.

05:40.840 --> 05:44.469
I've just had it with all
these movie stars showing off.

05:44.544 --> 05:46.978
"Look at me
and my black baby."

05:47.046 --> 05:49.514
Kill me. I want you to
stab me with something.

05:49.582 --> 05:52.551
You know, Kate,
not everyone is as tolerant

05:52.618 --> 05:55.280
of your alternative lifestyle
as we are.

05:56.522 --> 05:58.547
Being single is not
an alternative lifestyle.

05:58.624 --> 06:00.524
It is when you're 37.

06:03.329 --> 06:04.626
Oh, out like a light.

06:04.697 --> 06:06.221
Have you thought
about using a surrogate?

06:06.299 --> 06:07.891
<i>I saw a thing
about it on Dateline.</i>

06:07.967 --> 06:09.832
No, it's weird.
It's for weirdoes.

06:09.902 --> 06:11.392
I'm just gonna
keep trying by myself.

06:11.471 --> 06:14.929
Kate, building a family is not
like opening one of your stores.

06:15.007 --> 06:18.738
It's not an executive decision.
It's real life. It's messy.

06:18.811 --> 06:21.974
These hormone injections make me want
to punch you in the face right now.

06:22.048 --> 06:23.174
No hitting.

06:23.249 --> 06:24.546
That's right.
- You're right.

06:24.617 --> 06:26.551
There you go.
- Come on.

06:26.652 --> 06:29.348
Well, how much longer are you
gonna put your body through this?

06:29.422 --> 06:31.185
Look, I know for years
I said I didn't want one,

06:31.257 --> 06:33.054
but I just
woke up one day,

06:33.126 --> 06:36.857
and I felt like every baby on
the street was staring at me.

06:37.964 --> 06:40.330
Katie's coming out
of the mommy closet.

06:41.901 --> 06:43.425
Hey, Tyler.

06:43.503 --> 06:46.165
Tyler, what is this
all over you?

06:46.239 --> 06:48.264
Is that chocolate
or poop?

06:49.342 --> 06:51.367
