06:53.179 --> 06:54.771
It's chocolate.

06:56.215 --> 06:57.842
What if that
had been poop?

06:57.917 --> 07:00.147
I told you,
messy, but great.

07:14.567 --> 07:16.057
Not bad.

07:16.135 --> 07:18.000
Everybody do a shot
of this pea soup.

07:20.807 --> 07:24.174
Let's go with this.
Call it "Health Monster."

07:25.077 --> 07:27.102
That's great.

07:27.180 --> 07:28.738
