18:43.522 --> 18:47.185
<i>And in about two weeks, you
can take a home pregnancy test.</i>

18:50.596 --> 18:52.291
I live right here.

19:07.312 --> 19:09.007
Thanks for driving me
all the way home.

19:09.081 --> 19:11.549
