19:11.617 --> 19:13.414
Well, I would've
offered to do it anyway.

19:13.485 --> 19:15.544
Here, let me give you
some money for gas.

19:15.621 --> 19:17.486
No, no, please.
It's my treat.

19:17.556 --> 19:18.580
Really?

19:18.657 --> 19:20.284
Of course. Angie,
you don't understand.

19:20.359 --> 19:22.589
I want to be there for you
every step of the way.

19:26.098 --> 19:28.225
I hope you don't mind.
I bought you some groceries.

19:28.300 --> 19:31.133
I thought you might want
to start eating organic.

19:31.203 --> 19:34.036
That crap is for rich
people who hate themselves.

19:34.106 --> 19:35.971
Sorry, this place
is such a mess.

19:36.041 --> 19:37.906
I haven't had time
to clean up.

19:37.976 --> 19:41.434
No, it has a nice
old-timey smell.

19:43.582 --> 19:44.674
Is that an alligator?

19:44.750 --> 19:47.685
Hellboy?
No, that's Carl's iguana.

19:47.753 --> 19:51.655
Great. Well, I'm gonna put
this fruit in your refrigerator.

19:55.561 --> 19:56.653
